NOTE="filter-effects is enabled in wpt.json with the global includePrefixes filter (filter- / backdrop-filter / mix-blend-mode / isolation / Blending), exposing 122 layout-gradeable reftests to the layout-tree compare runner. 114 of 122 pass, including the filter-cb-abspos-inline-001/002/003 triplet that issue #64's group-1 fix recovered (filter now establishes an absolute-positioning containing block via the has_filter flag). The 8 known failures are the paint-side residuals issue #64 explicitly scopes out of layout containment: backdrop-filter geometry -- backdrop-filter-backdrop-root-clip-path-2 (root height 219.2 vs 400), -boundary (bg x 0 vs 504), -edge-pixels-2 (width 136.6 vs 100), -root-element (root height 600 vs 19.2), -nested-border-radius-clip-3 (width 220 vs 200); 3D perspective transform sizing under backdrop-filter -- backdrop-filter-3d-transform-perspective (card width 73.9 vs 100) and -nested-3d-transform-perspective (72.9 vs 100); and SVG <filter> subregion translate -- filter-subregion-01 (g x 200 vs 0). Pins 114/122 as a no-regression gate; closing the backdrop-filter / 3D-transform / SVG-subregion residuals is paint-side follow-up tracked in issue #64. Deterministic across two runs. Measured with the vendored Tinos text metric (tests/wpt-fonts)."
